  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Operate community mental health center in Pakistan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will help in operating mental health care center for one year in north-western Pakistan, providing a quality community-based mental health treatment &amp; community-based rehab services to poor &amp; needy men, women &amp; children with mental disorders in a decentralized and non-discriminative way. The project will relies on a close collaboration between patients, their families &amp; primary care providers within community settings for a better mental health, self-help and quality of life.</narrative>
  </description>
